对话武汉第一位出院的重症患者：这是我的第二次新生。
Dialogue Script3 3 Wuhan's first serious patient discharged from hospital: This is my second new life.
新京报记者。
Journalist, Beijing News.
新京报                      。
Beijing News.
新京报。
Beijing News.
